				\begin{document}$$A_{ji}^l$$\end{document}Ajil) is computed from the count of all paths that (1) connect voxel j and any voxel in seed area i, and (2) have an exact length of l. Each SFC matrix Al of size m-by-m can be recursively represented as follows:1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
